            <lg xml:id="TK1016">
<l>nāṇvēli koḷḷātu maṉṉō viyaṉñālam</l>
<l>pēṇalar mēlā yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great make modesty their barrier (of defence) and not the wide world.</l>
